{"tid":46803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【柏林恐襲】被捕貨車司機是難民 疑從波蘭偷車施襲","createTime":"2016-12-20T02:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T13:12:56.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ecfb9fb7f9982b94e57af84079b421e7e186859","tid":46803,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T02:02:19.000Z","msg":"德國柏林周一貨車撞聖誕市集事故，消息指被捕司機是難民，而貨車很可能是他從波蘭建築地盤偷來的。<br />\n<br />\n德國安全部門消息人士指，涉案司機來自阿富汗或巴基斯坦，今年2月抵德，曾犯輕微罪行，但不涉恐怖活動。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指疑犯用過不同名字，令核實身份工作難度增加。<br />\n<br />\n涉案貨車屬於波蘭一間貨運公司，車主茹拉夫斯基（Ariel Zurawski）指貨車原本運送鋼鐵，司機是他的表兄弟，但當地下午4時後與他失去聯絡。他否認被捕男子是他的司機，懷疑他騎劫了貨車。<br />\n<br />\n德新社／美聯社／路透社／法新社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56069458&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161220\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56069458%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161220&d=7Nc37eFySOEYvz6s2CRE7mN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=817cb2ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56069458%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161220&h=1275fe4c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56069458&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161220</a>"},{"pid":"3008e868ca783d08f7dfcedee7df5af91dd69aa8","tid":46803,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T02:03:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe76fd2bcf4aaff4c16f9aaa66f0980acdb0894a","tid":46803,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T02:04:36.000Z","msg":"多謝燒山"},{"pid":"69d915c6b068516a3b1dd09e1f1e98dc5bcd9490","tid":46803,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T02:04:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7738ZQa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F773